No prob, always glad to help.

::The Galactors::

If Supernova was in robot mode, he would have smiled sa he detected 
the EMP blasts heading for the two jets as the jets came toward each 
other. Even if he had tried to plan that, he couldn't have planned it 
better.

"Galactors, you know what to do!" he says, both jets seperating into 
seperate bots. The Galactors fly through the air toward each other, 
missing the EMP blasts fairly easily, though several almost get him 
by some. The Galactors reach each other, combining once again, but 
this time into different jets. Scrap was now with Vicyr and Slasys, 
and Supernova and Flare made up the other jet. Both jets angle 
upward, looking like an air show as they barely avoid colision with 
each other, zooming apart and still heading up. So far, the Galactor 
project was a success.
